title: Peaceful Lincoln Square 3 BR 2 bath with free laundry & parking option
map_address: Oakley Avenue near Oakley and Ainslie
posting_body: ["Sunny and spacious 3 BR 2 bath 1st floor duplex in renovated vintage 2-flat on beautiful tree-lined street just a stone's throw from the square.", 'Large living room and dining room with charming original built-in hutch.', 'Kitchen with white cabinetry and granite countertops, dishwasher, mini island, and cheery breakfast nook with scenic garden view.', 'Hardwood and ceramic tile flooring, central A/C. Free laundry and option to lease one garage parking space.', 'Bike storage in basement.', 'Quiet, safe, friendly, well maintained home.', 'Space suitable for up to 3 tenants, all bedrooms can accommodate queen bed.', '8 minute walk to Leland and Western brown line, quick walk to the square, Lincoln Ave and Damen Ave shops, restaurants, bars, and Winnemac Park.', 'To tour: Please respond to ad with your name, phone number, requested tour date(s), and best time I can call you to answer any questions you might have and to schedule your tour.', 'At time of tour, an application will be provided.', 'Credit score of 670 or higher requested.', 'Available 9/1/22.', ' Thank you!']
